tmjos-installer (1.3.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Bundles the .deb-based ubiquity installer for
    TMJOs ISOs, since Ubuntu 24.04's default installer is a snap
    (snapd is removed by TMJOs's slim phase).
  * Depends on ubiquity + ubiquity-frontend-gtk only — explicitly
    NOT on ubiquity-slideshow-ubuntu, which requires WebKit2GTK
    and crashed the installer on v1.3.0-1 ISO.
  * Postinst cleans /root/.config/pulse and /root/.cache to avoid
    permission-denied errors during ubiquity's rsync to target.
    These dirs get populated by PulseAudio during the Cubic build
    and then break the install pass.

 -- TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>  Sun, 10 May 2026 22:00:00 -0300
